   HILLS DEPARTMENT STORES Inc. (Canton, Mass.) -- John C.
Brouillard, 42 years old, was named to the new position of
executive vice president-chief financial officer of this
discount store chain. He was previously senior vice
president-finance and administration. Two others also were
named executive vice presidents: Eugene J. O'Donnell,
previously senior vice president-general merchandise manager;
and Andrew J. Samuto, previously senior vice president-real
estate development and human resources.
